Minimalistic style: A clean, elegant composition featuring three floating translucent presentation slides arranged in a cascading diagonal formation against a soft gradient background of deep navy to warm amber. Each slide casts subtle shadows and shows abstract geometric patterns of curly brackets and angular code-like shapes rendered as delicate embossed textures. Small luminous particles drift between the slides suggesting digital sharing and distribution. The overall mood is professional yet modern, with a sense of knowledge being released into the world.
